SIMPLE: unavoidable
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unavoidable
<hw>Un`a*void"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Not avoidable; incapable of being shunned or prevented; inevitable;
necessary; <as>as, <ex>unavoidable</ex> troubles</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>Not voidable; incapable of being
made null or void.</def> <rj><au>Blackstone.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Unavoidable hemorrhage</b></col> <fld>(Med.)</fld>,
<cd>hemorrhage produced by the afterbirth, or placenta, being situated
over the mouth of the womb so as to require detachment before the child
can be born.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un`a*void"a*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Un`a*void"a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unavoided</ent>⟦br⟧
